# Product Images Directory

Place your product images here with recommended specifications:
- **Dimensions:** 400x400 pixels (1:1 aspect ratio)
- **Format:** PNG (with transparency) or JPG
- **Size:** Under 500KB each
- **Background:** Clean, preferably white or transparent
- **Naming:** Use descriptive names (e.g., turmeric-powder.jpg)

## Usage Instructions

1. Add your product images to this folder
2. Import them in `/src/data/products.ts`
3. Update the product entries to use your images
4. Your images will automatically appear throughout the website

## Current Images
All current product images are imported from the parent `/src/assets/` folder and can be moved here for better organization.